.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">With a bit of woodwork, the humble door can look royal<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/wooden-bed-design-ideas\/\">7 Wooden Bed Design Ideas You Must Consider For Your Bedroom<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Collapsible Glass Master Bedroom Door Design for a Modern Touch<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Revitalise your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/master-bedroom-design-ideas\/\">master bedroom<\/a> with a contemporary touch using a collapsible glass master bedroom door design. The sleek glass panels embody the modern aesthetic, introducing a sense of openness and sophistication. This versatile door&#8217;s collapsible feature maximises space and functionality, making it an ideal choice for those seeking a contemporary and stylish upgrade to their master bedroom. Check out this space, which looks larger because of the glass door. The doors function as walls; on days you want openness, just prop them to the side and enjoy the abundant space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/07154838\/master-bedroom-door-design.jpg\" alt=\"Master bedroom door design with collapsible feature maximises space and functionality\" class=\"wp-image-56791\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/07154838\/master-bedroom-door-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/07154838\/master-bedroom-door-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/07154838\/master-bedroom-door-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/07154838\/master-bedroom-door-design-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-c